When we say this is a free (as in freedom) program, it doesn't mean
it's gratis. It means you have the freedom to use, study, share, and
modify it. In return, if you share modified versions, you must pass on
the same freedoms—attribution to the original author is required, and
you must release your modified source code under this same license.

